Wiring Diagram

MPU6050 Sensor
VCC: Connect to 3.3V or 5V (depending on your module)
GND: Connect to Ground
SDA: Connect to Arduino SDA (e.g., A4 on Uno)
SCL: Connect to Arduino SCL (e.g., A5 on Uno)

SSD1306 OLED Display
VCC: Connect to 3.3V or 5V
GND: Connect to Ground
SDA: Connect to same SDA as MPU6050
SCL: Connect to same SCL as MPU6050

Push Buttons
Menu Button (MENU_BTN):
One terminal to digital pin 3
Other terminal to Ground
Enter Button (ENTER_BTN):
One terminal to digital pin 4
Other terminal to Ground


Note: Both buttons use internal pull-up resistors.
